CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 14, 1958, pg. B7, reads: "TECH'S SCHOOL of Printing Management conferred one of its Bachelor of Science Degrees on Melvin Mister, center, of Chicago Ill."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of men wearing dark caps and gowns, including Melvin Mister third from end, recipient of Bachelor of Science Degree, at Carnegie Institute of Technology [Carnegie Mellon University] graduation
